        "content": "<p>I have the following goal state:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">ℝ</span>\n<span class=\"n\">ha</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">≤</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">-</span><span class=\"mi\">3</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>I'd like to derive <code>hb: x^2 ≥ 9</code> but am not succeeding.</p>\n<p>I have tried the following but it doesn't work.</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"k\">have</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">g1</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"bp\">^</span><span class=\"mi\">2</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">≥</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">9</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">by</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">rel</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">ha</span><span class=\"o\">]</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>Is the problem that the tactics like <code>rel</code> and <code>linarith</code>  only work with linear operations and not non-linear \"squared\" operations?</p>",
